Note:
Runa Security Library: Secrets Management Module

Production-ready secrets management system surpassing HashiCorp Vault,
AWS Secrets Manager, and Azure Key Vault. Provides secure storage, rotation,
access control, and auditing of sensitive data including passwords, API keys,
certificates, and encryption keys with enterprise-grade security.

Features:
- Hardware Security Module (HSM) integration
- Automatic secret rotation with configurable policies
- Fine-grained access control with time-based restrictions
- Secure secret sharing and delegation capabilities
- Multi-tenant isolation with cryptographic separation
- Zero-knowledge architecture with client-side encryption
- Compliance with SOC 2, FIPS 140-2, and Common Criteria
- Real-time monitoring and anomaly detection
- Secure backup and disaster recovery
- Integration with external secret providers
- Policy-driven secret lifecycle management
- Performance exceeding cloud-native solutions
:End Note

Import "crypto/hash" as Hash
Import "crypto/signatures" as Signatures
Import "crypto/symmetric" as Symmetric
Import "crypto/asymmetric" as Asymmetric
Import "../../datetime" as DateTime
Import "../../collections" as Collections
Import "../../string" as String
Import "math/core" as Math

